AUDIO: 'video help for suite load video node is great because you can do loads of things with it. You can set a custom FPS width, height, frame cap, and even where to start from. If you\'re loading images to'

[06:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'edit or just to use in your videos, you may like to resize them like this. We\'ve got a KJ nodes resize image V2 or another great option is to use the single load and resize node. Even though'

